# Enterprise AI Governance Policy

## 1. Objective
To ensure ethical and responsible use of Artificial Intelligence across all departments.

## 2. Scope
This policy applies to all employees and contractors using AI tools.

## 3. Data Privacy
- All training data must be anonymized.
- Data retention period is 5 years.

## 4. Bias Mitigation
- Dedicated Ethics Committee will perform quarterly bias testing.
- Manual review is required for high-risk models.

## 5. Computing
- R&D projects should leverage specialized GPU clusters.
